data.description: Nestled in a cul-de-sac, this beautiful home features three bedrooms, two baths, and a versatile office space suitable for use as an extra bedroom or serene retreat. Designed for seamless single-level living, this charming ranch residence epitomizes suburban tranquility, yet enjoys close proximity to schools, parks with pools and walking trails, and shopping centers for added convenience. Boasting stainless steel appliances, fresh flooring, newly renovated bathrooms, granite countertops, and a newer roof, this home offers a host of desirable features, promising both comfort and style.
